Requirements:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* UNIX-like operating system
  * VFS Support is not tested on Windows
* Apache >= 2.0
  * Modules: htaccess
* PHP >= 5.3
  * Modules: apache2 bcmath calendar curl curlwrappers gd inifile mysql snmp soap sockets sqlite3 sysvipc xmlreader xmlrpc xmlwriter xsl zip pdo imap mhash postgres tidy wddx mysqli intl pcntl
  * PHP.ini settings can be found in the top of 'header.php' file
* MySQL >= 5.0

Install Vendor Stuff:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Copy a X11's icon theme 16x16 and 32x32 folders into 'public_html/img/icons/'
* Install Propel ORM into 'vendor/Propel/' (By repository or archive)
* 'exiftool' is required for some API stuff
* 'pdf2svg' is required to read PDF files

First run:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* chown the 'public_html/media' directory to Apache user/group (recursive)
* chown the 'logs' directory to Apache user/group
* Run './bin/propel-gen' to initialize propel database setup
* Run './bin/propel-gen insert-sql' to set-up database tables etc

Update to latest revision:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Run './bin/update_revision'.
Note: You may have to change the script and set the appropriate Apache user/group
